(4, 1, 4, 51, NULL, 'The Nilgiri Mountain Railway', 'nilgiri mountain railway, vintage-themed train, toy train, world heritage site, culturalpalces, historic places, places to visit in tamil nadu, \r\n\r\n', 'The Nilgiri Mountain Railway, nicknamed the âToy Trainâ, excites kids more than anybody else. In 2005, UNESCO declared the railway as a World Heritage Site as an extension to the Darjeeling Himalayan Railway. It has since then been a part of the greater heritage site of the Mountain Railways in India.', 'the-nilgiri-mountain-railway', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(5, 1, 5, 62, NULL, 'Dharmapuri | City of Temples and Churches | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'dharmapuri, places to visit in tamil nadu, city of temples and churches, hogenakkal falls, tourist places in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism', 'Located on the North Western side of Tamil Nadu, Dharmapuri is often called the âCity of Temples and Churchesâ; thus making it a pilgrimage tourism hub with visitors from far and wide.', 'dharmapuri-district', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(6, 1, 6, 75, NULL, 'Ooty | Udhagamandalam | Hill stations in Tamil Nadu', 'popular hill stations in south india, hill stations in india, tourism destinations in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism, ooty, ootty, udhagamandalam, places to visit in ooty, ooty tourism, tamil nadu tourism, hill stations in tamil nadu, switzerland of india, toy train ride', 'Udhagamandalam or Ooty as it is famously known is a hill station in Tamil Nadu that nestles serenely in the Nilgiri District. ', 'ooty', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(7, 1, 7, 88, NULL, 'Madurai District | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'madurai, madurai temple, places to visit in madurai, thoonga nagaram, the city that never sleeps, meenakshi sundareswarar temple athens of the east, madurai meenakshi temple, pilgrim destinations in tamil nadu, places to visit in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism', 'Madurai is Tamil Naduâs culturally active and vibrant district. Its cultural heritage extends to more than 2,500 years from the great Tamil era. The district was an important cultural and commercial centre even as early as 550 AD. ', 'madurai-district', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(8, 1, 8, 99, NULL, 'The Nilgiri Mountain Railway | Toy Train |', 'nilgiri mountain railway, vintage-themed train, toy train, world heritage site, culturalpalces, historic places, places to visit in tamil nadu,', 'Imagine having a train ride through this region enjoying the glimpses of Nature at its best. That is what the Nilgiri Mountain Railway promises you. Nicknamed the âToy Trainâ as it excites kids more than anybody else, the railway line is a metre gauge that is 1000 mm long.', 'the-nilgiri-mountain-railway', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(9, 1, 9, 110, NULL, 'Gangai Konda Cholapuram | Shiva Temple | UNESCO World Heritage Site', 'gangai konda cholapuram, gangaikondacholeeswaram temple, unesco world heritage site, ancient temples of tamil nadu, heritage centres, monuments, unesco wonders, historical places', 'One of the largest temples in India, the Gangaikonda Cholapuram temple has Shiva as the principal deity. The main temple tower stands 55 m tall and the imposing building is covered in rich art and sculptures that adorn the premises in absolute grandeur', 'gangai-konda-cholapuram', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(10, 1, 10, 122, NULL, 'Toy Train Ride | Things to Do in Ooty | Tamil Nadu ', 'toy train, nilgiri mountain railway, ooty train ride, things to do in ooty, the nilgiris, unesco wonders in tamil nadu, unesco world heritage site in tamil nadu, toy train in ooty, must do things in tamil nadu, visit tamil nadu, ', 'One of the best things to do in Ooty is the Toy Train Ride. Nicknamed the âToy Trainâ as it excites kids more than anybody else, the railway line is a metre gauge that is 1000 mm long. ', 'toy-train-ride', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(11, 1, 27, 221, NULL, 'Airavatesvara Temple | Kumbhakonam | UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Tamil Nadu', 'airavatesvara temple, unesco world heritage sites in tamil nadu, must visit places in kumbhakonam, darasuram temple, unesco wonders in tamil nadu, heritage places, 12th century heritage temple, temple built by chola dynasty, airavatesvara temple unesco, airavatesvara temple history, airavatesvara temple mystery', 'The grand Airavastesvara Temple in Kumbakonam is a treasure-trove of history, facts and amazing art. The construction of the temple, which is now a UNSECO World Heritage Site, dates back to the 12th century CE and was built by the renowned Chola king Rajaraja Chola II.', 'airavatesvara-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
