(176, 1, 231, 1941, NULL, 'Ooty Lake | Tourist Destinations | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Ooty Lake, places to visit in ooty, ooty tourism, things to do in ooty, boating in ooty lake, ooty lake tour, ', 'There are many fun activities that tourists can indulge in when they are at the Ooty Lake. Cycles are available for rent to ride around the Lake. Boating is another attraction.  A tranquil ride through the waters is an attractive pastime as it lets one take in the entire beauty of the Lake', 'ooty-lake', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
