(199, 1, 270, 2222, NULL, 'Mountain Biking  | Adventure Tourism | Things to Do in Tamil Nadu', 'Mountain Biking, adventure tourism, things to do in tamil nadu, ooty mountain biking, maountain biking in tamil nadu, ', 'Hop on your bike and head to the hills to dance on the undulations and zip down the slopes. Tamil Nadu offers a variety of biking trails for adrenaline junkies to relish in the joy of mountain biking.', 'mountain-biking', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(200, 1, 271, 2229, NULL, 'Off Roading | Things to do in Tamil Nadu', 'Off Roading, off road drives in tamil nadu, adventure tourism in tamil nadu, things t do in tamil nadu, places to go off road rides in tamil nadu, mahabalipuram off roading, kolukkumalai off road rides,', 'From the sandy beaches of the East Coast to the slushy slopes of the Ghats, Tamil Nadu has no dearth of off-road challenges. Hop on your 4X4s and adventure bikes, and head on to explore the uncharted and unpaved tracks all over Tamil Nadu.', 'off-roading', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(201, 1, 272, 2236, NULL, 'Para Sailing | Adventure Tourism | Things to Do in Tamil Nadu', 'Para Sailing, adventure tourism tamil nadu, things t do in tamil nadu, places to do parasailing, para sailing in rameswara, para sailing in marina beach, chennai ecr para sailing adventures, ', 'Ever dreamt of being able to fly like a bird and glide over some of the most beautiful landscapes in Tamil Nadu? Well, parasailing is the easiest way to realize that dream. With the enchanting views of some of the iconic and beautiful landscapes and beaches, Tamil Nadu will be a memorable experience that you can add to your bucket list.\r\n', 'para-sailing', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
