(222, 1, 293, 2525, NULL, 'Coimbatore | City | Manchester of South India | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'coimbatore, coimbatore city, places to visit in coimbatore, things to do in coimbatore, visit coimbatore, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Coimbatore is home to a large number of textile units, earning it the nickname âManchester of the Southâ. Apart from textile, the city has a number of engineering industries, two special economic zones, automobile units, electronics and various other successful manufacturing facilities. Apart from the buzzing present and a promising future, Coimbatore has a rich history too', 'coimbatore', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(223, 1, 294, 2541, NULL, 'Madurai | Cities of Tamil Nadu | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'madurai, places to visit in tamil nadu, madurai city, places to visit in madurai, things to do in madurai, visit madurai, madurai tourism, temples in madurai, tamil nadu tourism, thoonga nagaram', 'Referred to as the âAthens of the Eastâ due to the lofty towers of Meenakshi Sundareswarar Temple just like the Greek Pantheon, the city finds reference in many literary works of Arabs, Romans and Greek travellers like Megasthenes. Madurai also finds a place in âSilapathigaramâ, a Sangam literature work.', 'madurai', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(224, 1, 295, 2557, NULL, 'Kunthukal Beach | Beaches in Rameswaram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Kunthukal beach, beaches in tamil nadu, places to visit in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism, rameswaram, beaches in rameswaram, pampan island, kunthukal fishing village, beaches in rameswaram, places to visit in rameswaram, Vivekananda Memorial Hall, ', 'One of the factors that make Kunthukal Beach so popular is its amazing location. Tucked away in the serene Pampan Island in Rameshwaram, Kunthukal Beach is the heart of the fishing village of Kunthukal. Itâs a dream vacation spot for both Indian and international tourists alike', 'kunthukal-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
