(258, 1, 337, 3081, NULL, 'Maruthamalai Murugan Temple | Subramanya Swami Temple | Coimbatore | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Maruthamalai Arulmigu Subramanya Swami Temple, Maruthamalai Murugan Temple', 'Maruthamalai Murugan Temple in Coimbatore district is flocked by thousands of devotees round the year. This 12th century temple is dedicated to Lord Murugan and is considered as one of the seventh houses of him. Like most other Murugan Temples, this shrine is also placed upon a hillock. ', 'maruthamalai-murugan-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(259, 1, 338, 3094, NULL, 'Thengapattinam Beach | Kanyakumari district | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Thengapattinam Beach, Thengapattanam, beaches in Tamil Nadu, Kanyakumari, Tamil Nadu tourism', 'Thengapattinam Beach is located in the coastal village of Paimkulam in Kanyakumari district. Pristine blue waters, sun-kissed beaches with warm sands and an array of coconut trees welcome you as you step into the Thengapattinam Beach.', 'thengapattinam-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
