(262, 1, 341, 3133, NULL, 'Guna Caves | Kodaikanal | Dindigul District | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Guna Caves, kodaikanala, places to visit in kodaikanal, visit kodaikanal, tourist destinations in dindigul, dindigul tourism, tourist places in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism', 'Situated at an altitude of 2,200 metres, the Guna Caves is a thing of mystery and wonder that attracts travellers in hordes. Earlier known as \'Devilâs Kitchen\', the place got its name \'Guna\' after the 1992 Tamil blockbuster movie Guna was shot here.', 'guna-caves', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(263, 1, 342, 3147, NULL, 'Sri Ekambareswar Temple | Kancheepuram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Sri Ekambareswar Temple', 'The Ekambareswar Temple is the most popular and the largest temple in Kancheepuram district, dating back to nearly 600 to 700 years, and dedicated to lord Siva. Three major dynasties - the Chola, the Pandavas and the Vijaynagar Empire contributed towards the construction of this temple. The temple is also considered as one of the Pancha Bhootha Sthalam (five elements) temple existing in Tamil Nadu.', 'ekambareswar-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(264, 1, 343, 3161, NULL, 'Kailasanathar Temple | Kancheepuram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Kailasanathar Temple', 'The Kailasanathar temple, also known as the Kailasanatha temple, is a Pallava-era historic Hindu temple in Kancheepuram, Tamil Nadu, India. Dedicated to Shiva, the monument reflects a Dravidian architecture and was built about 700 CE by Narasimhavarman II with additions by Mahendra III.', 'kailasanathar-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(265, 1, 344, 3175, NULL, 'Varadharaja Perumal Temple | Kancheepuram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Varadharaja Perumal Temple', 'Varadharaja Perumal Temple is a Hindu temple dedicated to Vishnu located in the holy city of Kancheepuram, Tamil Nadu, India. It is one of the Divya Desams, the 108 temples of Vishnu believed to have been visited by the 12 poet saints, or Alwars.', 'varadharaja-perumal-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(266, 1, 345, 3189, NULL, 'The Kamakshi Amman Temple | Kancheepuram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Kamakshi Amman Temple', 'The Kamakshi Amman Temple is an ancient Hindu Temple dedicated to Kamakshi, the ultimate Goddess Lalita Maha Tripura Sundari. It is located in the historic city of Kancheepuram in Kancheepuram district. The Temple was most probably built by the Pallava kings, whose capital was Kancheepuram. The Dravidian architecture of the monument leaves travellers and pilgrims absolutely awestruck.', 'kamakshi-amman-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(267, 1, 346, 3203, NULL, 'Sri Ulagalandha Perumal Temple | Kancheepuram | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Sri Ulagalandar Temple', 'Sri Ulagalandha Perumal Temple, dedicated to Vishnu, is located in Kancheepuram district, Tamil Nadu, India. Constructed in the Dravidian style of architecture, the temple is glorified in the Divya Prabandha, the early medieval Tamil canon of the Azhwar saints from the 6th through 9th centuries CE. The presiding deity, Lord Vishnu is projected in Vamana form in the temple.', 'sri-ulagalandha-perumal-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
