(287, 1, 367, 3490, NULL, 'Avalanche Lake, Ooty | The Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'avalanche lake, ooty, ooty, ooty tourism, lakes in tamil nadu, the nilgiris, places to visit in nilgiris, things to do in ooty, ooty tourism, tamil nadu tourism, visit ooty, ', 'Imagine waking up to a dreamlike sunrise over the misty mountains and spending a whole day hiking through lush woods and fishing in the blue waters of a serene lake. The Avalanche Lake in Ooty has that and more to offer to travellers looking to be lost in the beauty of nature.\r\n', 'avalanche-lake-ooty', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(288, 1, 368, 3504, NULL, 'Doddabetta, Ooty | The Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Doddabetta, Ooty, hill stations in ooty, visit ooty, places to visit in ooty, ooty tourism, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Countless rugged and rustic trails winding through hillocks and countryside for around 10 kms from the Ooty town will take you to the foot of Doddabetta where you will be welcomed by a steep climb. The seemingly challenging trail amidst green slopes of the peak will prove effortless as it gets you closer to the clouds. ', 'doddabetta-ooty', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(289, 1, 369, 3518, NULL, 'Ketty Valley View | Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Ketty Valley View, ooty, places to visit in ooty, things to do in the nilgiris, connoor, the nilgiris, visit ooty, ', 'Ketty Valley blesses travellers with a breath-taking view and an opportunity to explore its countless serene hamlets. Ketty Valley is a popular destination amongst travellers in search of inner peace and the solace of nature. Blessed with surreal vistas of the rolling blue hills of Nilgiris and the unending greenery, Ketty Valley is a perfect weekend getaway destination. ', 'ketty-valley-view', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
