(243, 1, 404, 3970, '<p>Chennai is a destination of many moods. On one side there is the bustling metropolitan city, on another part is the quaint and historic locations that add to the charm of the region, and then there are amazingly serene spots that attract tourists from far and wide. Among all these, the beaches play an important part in making Chennai a must-visit city. One of the most picturesque and serene beaches among these is the Thiruvanmiyur Beach.</p>\r\n<p>Located in the neighbourhood of Thiruvanmiyur in Chennai, the beach is a spot for various activities. Despite being a part of the city, the beach is clean and well-maintained, providing the right ambiance for visitors to relax and enjoy. Thiruvanmiyur beach is also one of the most quiet and isolated beaches in Chennai, making it ideal to enjoy the stunning view of the sea. Many people visit the spot to enjoy the sunset view that is quite breathtaking. Smart bike cycling is one initiative that is of attraction here. You can experience the view of the beach by renting cycles and going around. Thiruvanmiyur beach is also a perfect spot for beach sports, if you are into such entertainments. Whether football, volleyball or the local favourite cricket, the beach will for sure be a perfect host. There are many snacking options around the beach and you will get to try some of the finest regional delicacies in the destination.</p>\r\n<p>So, do make it a point to visit and experience Thiruvanmiyur Beach on your trip to Chennai.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
