(1, 1, 1, 8, NULL, 'Mamallapuram Shore Temple | UNESCO World Heritage Sites in Tamil Nadu', 'mamallapuram shore temple, unesco world heritage sites in tamil nadu, shore temple tamil nadu, mahabalipuram shore temple, alaivay-k-kovil, eight shrines, hindu monument, pallava temple, ancient temples of tamil nadu, heritage centres, monuments, unesco wonders, historical places ', 'Mamallapuram Shore Temple, believed to be built during the reign of the old Pallavan king Rajasimha/Narasimhavarman II, is one of the oldest temples of significance in South India. The Shore Temple complex was designated as a UNESCO World Heritage Site along with other temples and monuments of Mamallapuram.', 'mamallapuram-shore-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
