(95, 1, 137, 1227, NULL, 'Mukurthi National Park | Wildlife | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Mukurthi National Park, UNESCO World Heritage Site, Nilgiri Tahr, Nilgiri Tahr National Park, wildlife sanctuaries in tamil nadu, tamil nadu wildlife, visit tamil nadu wildlife, mukurthi national park is the sanctuary for, mukurthi national park is famous for, mukurthi national park river, mukurthi national park stay, mukurthi national park trekking', 'Spread across an area of 78.46 sq. km., the Mukurthi National Park is a UNESCO World Heritage Site, as a part of the Western Ghats. The park was created with an intent to protect the Nilgiri Tahr, one of the keystone species found commonly in the Nilgiris and was previously known as the Nilgiri Tahr National Park.', 'mukurthi-national-park', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(96, 1, 138, 1242, NULL, 'Anamalai Tiger Reserve | Wildlife | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Anamalai Tiger Reserve, tiger reserve in tamil nadu, tamil nadu wildlife, wildlife sanctuaries in tamil nadu, Indira Gandhi Wildlife Sanctuary and National Park, Anamalai Hills, places to visit in Pollachi, anamalai tiger reserve room booking, anamalai tiger reserve stay, anamalai tiger reserve upsc, anamalai tiger reserve resorts, mudumalai and anamalai tiger reserve, anamalai tiger reserve, pollachi contact number, how to reach anamalai tiger reserve, anamalai tiger reserve photos', 'As the name suggests, Anamalai Tiger Reserve is primarily a sanctuary for the preservation of tigers. However, the area is home to a wide variety of fauna and flora that attract tourists from far and wide.', 'anamalai-tiger-reserve', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
