(306, 1, 390, 3776, NULL, 'Valparai | Hill Station | Coimbatore | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Valparai, valparai hill station, places to visit in coimbatore, Upper Sholayar Dam,Nirar Dam, Aliyar Dam, Monkey Falls , Balaji temple (Karimalai), Velankanni Church (Karimalai), Pancha Mugha Vinayagar Koil (Near Sholayar), chinnakkal, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Located at 3500 feet height from the sea level on the Anamalai mountain range of the Western Ghats, Valparai prides itself as one of the first choice tourist destinations. Even with its rustic charm, the place is well connected. Enjoy the drive to Valparai along the hairpin curves and marveling at the hilly ranges filled with greenery. ', 'valparai-hill-station', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
