(318, 1, 402, 3945, NULL, 'Kanyakumari Beach | Destinations  Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Kanyakumari Beach, Kanyakumari beach, sunrise at kanyakumari, places to visit in kanyakumari, kanyakumari sunset, beaches in kanyakumari, visit kanyakumari, kanyakumari tourism, tamil nadu tourism ttdc, places to visit in tamil nadu, ', 'Located at the southernmost coast of the Indian peninsula, Kanyakumari Beach offers attractions that are highly unique. Here is where you can see the confluence of three major water bodies that in many ways define this uniqueness â the Bay of Bengal, the Indian Ocean and the Arabian Sea. ', 'kanyakumari-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
