(320, 1, 404, 3975, NULL, 'Thiruvanmiyur Beach | Destinations | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Thiruvanmiyur Beach, beaches in chennai, places o visit in chennai, chennai tourism, tamil nadu tourism, less explored places in chennai, ', 'Located in the neighbourhood of Thiruvanmiyur in Chennai, the beach is a spot for various activities. Despite being a part of the city, the beach is clean and well-maintained, providing the right ambiance for visitors to relax and enjoy. Thiruvanmiyur beach is also one of the most quiet and isolated beaches in Chennai, making it ideal to enjoy the stunning view of the sea. ', 'thiruvanmiyur-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
