(367, 1, 520, 4910, NULL, 'Fort St. George | Forts in Chennai | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Fort St. George, st marys church, St. George fort museum, places to visit in tamil nadu, places to visit in chennai, chennai tourism, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Called the White Town, the St. George Fort was built in the 1640s to protect the trade interests of the East India Company, a brutal British trading firm with a private army that conquered, subjugated and plundered India for more than a century.', 'fort-st-george', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
