(370, 1, 523, 4964, NULL, 'Sanguthurai Beach | Beaches | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'Sanguthurai beach, saugathurai beach in kanyakumari, beaches in kanyakumar, kanyakumari tourism, places to visit in kanyakumari, tamil nadu tourism,', 'Considered to be one of the cleanest beaches in Kanyakumari, Sanguthurai Beach offers unique views of the sea. The majesty of the Vivekananda Rock Memorial and Thiruvalluvar Statue can be experienced from this shore. ', 'sanguthurai-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(371, 1, 524, 4981, NULL, 'Velankanni Beach | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'velankanni beach', 'One of the most scenic beaches in the east coast of Tamil Nadu, the Velankanni Beach is a picture-perfect and bustling holiday spot. Millions of people visit the beach every year, both as a part of their pilgrimage and even for sightseeing purposes. If you like the busy beach ambiance, then Velankanni is for sure a good place to be in. ', 'velankanni-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(372, 1, 525, 4997, NULL, 'Annai Indira Gandhi Road Bridge | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'annai indira gandhi road bridge, rameswaram, places to visit in rameswarm, rameswaram bridge, pammaban bridge, dhanuskodi, ', 'The Annai Indira Gandhi Road Bridge connects the National Highway (NH 49) with Rameswaram on Pamban Island. This spectacular road bridge surrounded by the calm sea and which runs parallel to the Pamban rail bridge was inaugurated by the former Indian Prime Minister Rajiv Gandhi in 1988.\r\n', 'annai-indira-gandhi-road-bridge', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(373, 1, 526, 5016, NULL, 'Ram Sethu Bridge | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'ram sethu bridge, rameswaram, tamilnadu tourism, places to visit in tamil nadu, rameshwaram tourism', 'Rameswaram has a vast number of pilgrims visiting its religious destinations as it is considered one of the four holy sites (Char Dham) among Hindus. One such destination that has significant religious importance in Rameswaram is the Ram Sethu bridge. \r\n', 'ram-sethu-bridge', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
