(394, 1, 547, 5283, NULL, 'Munthiri Kothu | Tamil Nadu', 'munthiri kothu', 'Munthiri Kothu is a traditional sweet recipe which is also popular in Kerala. This can be a guilt-free indulgence for those who are health-conscious and yet have a major sweet craving. This snack doesnât contain any refined sugar and is made using green gram and jaggery coated with a layer of rice batter and deep-fried.', 'munthiri-kothu', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
