(403, 1, 556, 5391, NULL, 'Sathamudhu (Kalyana Rasam) | Tamil Nadu', 'sathamudhu (kalyana rasam)', 'The Sathamudhu or Kalyana rasam is a special variation of rasam found in the meals of the Tamil Brahmin cuisine, made using freshly ground spices and tomatoes. The Kalyana rasam is different from the other grand dishes accompanying a meal, with its simple, mild and tangy flavour. It is also known as âPoricha rasamâ and is said to taste heavenly with piping hot rice and an appalam (pappad).', 'sathamudhu-kalyana-rasam', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1);
