(404, 1, 557, 5403, NULL, 'Curd Rice | Tamil Nadu', 'curd rice', 'Curd rice is a healthy comfort food in Tamil Nadu that is usually consumed with just pickles as accompaniment. Since curd is a natural coolant, curd rice works best for the hot weather in Tamil Nadu and is an effortless recipe that anybody can whip up. Curd rice is probiotic, refreshing and also an integral part of a brahmin meal.', 'curd-rice', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(405, 1, 558, 5415, NULL, 'Thirattippal | Tamil Nadu', 'thirattippal', 'The Thirattippal or Palkova is a drool-worthy traditional dessert from Tamil Nadu that requires just two ingredients to prepare â condensed milk and jaggery. The dish has its origin in Srivilliputhur, a town in Tamil Nadu famous for its milk sweets and delicacies. Flavouring ingredients like cardamom, cashews and ghee can also be used to prepare Thirattippal but the authentic recipe requires just milk and jaggery. Though the process is time-consuming, the heavenly aroma and taste of Thirattippal', 'thirattippal', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(406, 1, 580, 5499, NULL, 'St. Stephenâs Church | Tamil Nadu', 'st. stephenâs church', 'A church of great antiquity and impeccable architectural beauty, St. Stephenâs Church is a remarkable landmark of Ooty that is a window into the long history of the queen of hill stations. The church, embellished with beautiful stained-glass windows and antique features, is a jewel in the crown of the queen of Nilgiris.\r\n', 'st-stephens-church', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(407, 1, 581, 5516, NULL, 'Arulmigu Dhandayuthapani Swamy Temple, Palani | Tamil Nadu', 'arulmigu dhandayuthapani swamy temple, palani, temples in tamil nadu, pilrim centres, must visit temple in tamil nadu, palani murugan kovil, ', 'As per Hindu mythology, Lord Muruga came to Palani as he failed in the task given by Sage Narada. He, along with his brother Ganesha was asked to encircle the world thrice and the first person who comes before the sage after this task was to be offered the gnana-palam or the fruit of knowledge.', 'arulmigu-dhandayuthapani-swamy-temple-palani', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(408, 1, 582, 5533, NULL, 'Kodaikanal Lake | Dindigul | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'kodaikanal lake, lakes in tamil nadu, kodaikanal tourism, places to visit in dindigul, tamil nadu tourism, tourist places in tamil nadu, visit tamil nadu', 'The fame of Kodaikanal lake or Kodai lake has travelled across states and it has become one of the favourite photographic spots and movie locations, even in Bollywood. There are resorts and hotels available around the lake where you can accommodate yourself enjoying the tranquillity of the lake and the enticing landscape around it.\r\n\r\n', 'kodaikanal-lake', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(409, 1, 583, 5550, NULL, 'Coakerâs Walk | Kodaikanal | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'coakerâs walk, places to visit in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism, kodaikanal, koadikanal tourism, things to do in kodaikanal, places to visit in kodaikanal, tamil naduu tourism, trip to koadai, koadi, ', 'Enjoy a mystic walk among the clouds at the Coakers walk, near Kodaikanal Lake. Nature enthusiasts and shutterbugs should never miss the place for the view and ambience it offers. Open from 7 am and 7 pm, the walkway is very near the Kodaikanal Lake.', 'coakers-walk', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(410, 1, 657, 5795, NULL, 'Shooting Point, Ooty | The Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'shooting point, ooty, the nilgiris, ooty tourism, Wenlock Downs, shooting medu, 9 th mile shooting point ooty, places to visit in ooty, ooty tourism, visit ooty, tamil nadu tourism, the nilgiris tourism, ', 'Have you ever wanted to visit fairy-tale-like settings and recreate iconic scenes from your favourite movies? Head to Shooting Point in Ooty, where a picturesque view of unending green meadows and rolling hills veiled in thin white fog awaits you.\r\n', 'shooting-point-ooty', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(411, 1, 658, 5814, NULL, 'Pillar Rocks | Tamil Nadu', 'pillar rocks', 'Are you an adventure lover and want to try out trekking, mountain climbing and rock climbing?! A three to four hours of trekking through the thick fogs and woods before reaching Pillar rocks offers you nothing less than an enthralling adventurous experience!', 'pillar-rocks', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(412, 1, 659, 5831, NULL, 'Shembaganur Museum of Natural History | Kodaikanal | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'shembaganur museum of natural history, kodaikanal museum, natural history museum in kodaikanal, places to visit in kodaikanal, dindigul tourism, tourist places in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Want to see the exotic and extinct species of animals and birds of Kodaikanal? Head to the 127-year-old Shembagunar museum of natural history, where species of animals and birds of Kodaikanal, are preserved. The extensive lab-like museum also has one of the best orchidariums in the country and fossils of wildlife creatures. \r\n\r\n', 'shembaganur-museum-of-natural-history', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(413, 1, 707, 5991, NULL, 'Gudalur | The Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'gudalur, tamil nadu tourism, hill stations in tamil nadu, the nilgiris, places to visit in nilgiris, tea plantations in nilgiris, ', 'Gudalur in the Nilgiris district has it all. Picturesque mountains, valleys, evergreen forests, tea and coffee plantations, all of which make this less-explored locality a compelling destination.', 'gudalur', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(414, 1, 708, 6008, NULL, 'Masinagudi  | The Nilgiris | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'masinagudi, the nilgiris, hill stations in tamilnadu, tamil nadu tourism, places to visit in tamil nadu, masinagudi wildlife, ', 'Masinagudi is an experience no wildlife enthusiasts should ever miss. A captivating hill station on the Nilgiri mountains, Masinagudi is a part of the Mudumalai National Park situated on the road that connects Mysore and Ooty.', 'masinagudi', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(415, 1, 709, 6030, NULL, 'Poombarai | Kodaikanal | Dindigul | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'poombarai, hill stations in tamil nadu, places to visit in kodaikanal, kodaikanal tourism, poombarai village, adventure tourism in poombarai, dindigul tourism, ', 'Known as Kodaikanalâs best kept secret, Poombarai is another picturesque village in Kodai hills that has stunning terraced landscapes enveloped by green mountains and valleys', 'poombarai', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(416, 1, 710, 6047, NULL, 'Kolukkumalai | Theni | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'kolukkumalai, worlds highest tea estate, kolukkumala trekking, kolukkumala camping, kolukkumara sunrise point, places to visit in theni, tamil nadu tourism, ', 'Situated near Munnar is this world\'s highest tea plantation known as Kolukkumalai, a hamlet in Theni district in Tamil Nadu. ', 'kolukkumalai', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(417, 1, 711, 6067, NULL, 'The Cardamom hills | Kodaikanal | Tamil Nadu', 'the cardamom hills - kodaikanal, places to visit in kodaikanal, kodaikanal tourist destiations, hill in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism, kodaikanal tourism, visit kodaikanal, ', 'The Cardamom hills denotes the entire Western Ghats range that lies south of the Palghat gap. Lying in both Kerala and Tamil Nadu, the crest of the hills form the boundary between the two states.', 'the-cardamom-hills-kodaikanal', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(418, 1, 712, 6087, NULL, 'Veena | Art & Crafts | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'veena, veena making in tamil nadu, thanjavur veena, Thanjavur Veena is the first musical instrument in the country to get the GI , arts and crafts in tamil nadu, musical instruments in tamil nadu, tamil nadu tourism', 'One of the ancient instruments in India, the Veena holds a prime position in classical music instruments. Thanjavur in Tamil Nadu is famed for being the hub of making the instrument. Here the artisans have been handcrafting the Veena for generations. The Thanjavur Veena is the first musical instrument in the country to get the GI (Geographical Indication) tag.\r\n', 'veena', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(419, 1, 716, 6112, NULL, 'Vattakottai Beach | Kanyakumari | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'vattakottai beach, beaches in tamil nadu, vattakottai fort, vattakottai, kanyakumari, places to visit in kanyakumari, ', 'A sun-kissed beach that is located near to a glowing historic location; a venue to unwind and relax from the buzzes of city life. Welcome to Vattakottai Beach, one of the finest and most captivating beaches in Kanyakumari.\r\n', 'vattakottai-beach', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(420, 1, 719, 6131, NULL, 'Veena | Arts & Crafts | Tamil Nadu Tourism', 'veena, arts and crafts, things to do, experiences,  thanjavur veena, gi tag veena, ', 'One of the ancient instruments in India, the Veena holds a prime position in classical music instruments. Thanjavur in Tamil Nadu is famed for being the hub of making the instrument. Here the artisans have been handcrafting the Veena for generations. The Thanjavur Veena is the first musical instrument in the country to get the GI (Geographical Indication) tag.', 'veena', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
(421, 1, 725, 6156, NULL, 'Adi Keshava Perumal Temple | Tamil Nadu', 'adi keshava perumal temple, temples in kanyakumari, places to isit in kanyakumari, kanyakumari tourism, tamil nadu tourism, tamil nadu, visit tamil nadu, pilgrim centres in tamil nadu, ', 'A quaint temple nestling in a splendid spot, emanating the vibrant charm of the good old days; with the glorious idol of Lord Vishnu resting serenely in the sanctum sanctorum. Adi Keshava Perumal Temple attracts pilgrims and visitors from far and wide.\r\n', 'adi-keshava-perumal-temple', NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', 1),
